Bundle::Melody::Test is a bundle containing the
prerequisite CPAN modules for testing and other diagnostic 
features in Melody [http://openmelody.org/]. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make 
    make test 
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

By definition a Bundle is a list of dependencies. See the
POD documentation in the extlib.pm module for a list of
packages.

